                     <interp inst="t18030112-12-person109" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I was with Read; I know no more than he does.(The handkerchief was produced, and identified by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner left his defence to his Counsel; and called one witness, who gave him a good character. <rs id="t18030112-12-verdict63" type="verdictDescription">
